<head>漢譯南傳大藏經 註解</head>
<p>
<note n="0312001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0312001">雜阿含經卷四五．一八（大正藏二．三三一b）。</note>
<note n="0312002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0312002">師今不在故我不能止。</note>
<note n="0313003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0313003">雜阿含經卷四五．一六（大正藏二．三三〇c）。</note>
<note n="0313004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0313004">如斯之人，到達 vihāragaruko 屋室。</note>
<note n="0313005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0313005">直至翌晨托鉢時，猶在室中。</note>
<note n="0314006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0314006">vanatha = kilesamahāvana（煩惱大林）。</note>
<note n="0314007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0314007">底本之 anato 讀作 arati = taṇhārati rahito。</note>
<note n="0314008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0314008">mutattā = viññāṇattabhāvā。</note>
<note n="0314009" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0314009">依 upadhi = khandha-kilesa-abhisankhāra 諸蘊、煩惱行之諸依。</note>
<note n="0314010" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0314010">底本之 saṭṭhitaritā 讀作 saṭṭhi nissitā。註釋為執著於六境之凡常不如法覺。其六境之一一各有十覺。</note>
<note n="0315011" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0315011">paṭicca 在註釋中則解釋為 nibbānaṁ paṭicca。</note>
<note n="0315012" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0315012">雜阿含經卷四五．一九（大正藏二．三三一c）。</note>
<note n="0316013" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0316013">vijjāyantakaro = vijjāya kilesa-antakaro。</note>
<note n="0316014" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0316014">samitāvi = rāgâdinaṁ samitatāya samitāvi。</note>
<note n="0316015" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0316015">雜阿含經卷四五．一七（大正藏，二．三三一c）。</note>
<note n="0317016" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0317016">原文 parato passa 如依字義為見他，在註釋則作見無常解。</note>
<note n="0317017" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0317017">sati kāyagatā 身念住，乃觀身不淨。</note>
<note n="0317018" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0317018">現觀於慢。乃現觀於慢之捨離。（註釋）</note>
<note n="0317019" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0317019">雜阿含經卷四五．二一（大正藏二．三三二a）。</note>
<note n="0319020" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0319020">雜阿含經卷四五．一三（大正藏二．三二九b）。</note>
<note n="0320021" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0320021">雜阿含經卷四五．一五（大正藏二．三三〇a）。</note>
<note n="0322022" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0322022">雜阿含經卷四五．二二（大正藏二．三三二b）。</note>
<note n="0322023" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0322023">原文 nibbānapaṭisaṁyutta 乃與涅槃相關之義。</note>
<note n="0324024" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0324024">在底本雖作 asitaṁ，在註釋中則讀作 anissitaṁ。漢譯亦作清白之法，今譯作無所著之清白法。</note>
<note n="0324025" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0324025">依註示，見處者，乃指識處之四識住，七識住，亦指我人之輪迴。</note>
<note n="0325026" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0325026">在註中，解釋其五之第一法，說示五群之首，五群之法，其意義則不甚明瞭。在英譯中，則讀作 dassa-ṭ ṭhānaṁ。</note>
